Sieve.Plus
Copyright 2025 Alex (uldahlalex)

This project is a fork of and based upon Sieve:
https://github.com/Biarity/Sieve

Original Sieve Copyright 2018 Biarity, 2021 Ashish Patel and Kevin Sommer

Changes from the original Sieve project include:
- Added OR query support using || (double pipe) operator for flexible filtering
- Created type-safe query builder functionality (Sieve.Plus.QueryBuilder package)
- Extended multi-framework support to include net9.0
- Enhanced filter parsing to support complex OR/AND combinations
- Maintained full backward compatibility with original Sieve API

